### Description

Another good feature that would be awesome in templates would be *deconstruction* of arrays and objects.

### Proposed solution

for example

```ts
export interface Person
{
    name: string;
    surname: string;
    age: number;
    address: string;
}

```

```html
@for({name, surname} of persons; track surname)
{
     <div>NAME: {{name}}</div>
     <div>SURNAME: {{surname}}</div>
}
```

or with `let` syntax

```html
@let {name} = person;
```

same with arrays
```html
@let [firstPerson] = persons;
```

